gameRecap.title: Game Recap: 76ers 121, Nets 99
gameRecap.excerpt: The 76ers defeated the Nets, 121-99. Joel Embiid recorded 32 points, 12 rebounds, and nine assists for the 76ers, with Tyrese Maxey adding 25 points and 10 assists in the victory. Lonnie Walker IV tallied 26 points and six rebounds for the Nets in the losing effort. The 76ers improve to 10-3 in the regular season, while the Nets fall to 6-7.
